 *  Employee Business Management System — C++ Backend
 *  Compile: g++ -std=c++17 -o server backend.cpp
 *  Run:     ./server          (listens on port 8080)
 * ============================================================
 *
 *  OOP Concepts Used:
 *   - Inheritance      : Accountant, Cook, Assistant → Employee
 *   - Virtual methods  : getRole(), getRoleCode(), display()
 *   - Constructors     : parameterised + copy constructors
 *   - Destructors      : virtual destructor in base class
 *   - Encapsulation    : private data, public accessors/mutators
 *   - Polymorphism     : vector<Employee*> holds mixed subtypes
 *   - Abstract concept : Employee has pure-virtual getRole()
 * ============================================================
 */

